						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Pillar in the Kallēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Prabhava, Sunday, Amāvāsya, Solar eclipse, Saṁkramaṇa,</hi> the details being not enough for verification. It may be assigned to about the <hi rend="bold">13th Century A.D.</hi> on palaeographical grounds.</p>						

						<p>The inscription records a gift of a charity-house for the benefit of the temple of Kalidēva at <hi rend="bold">Hosavura</hi> by <hi rend="italic">pradhāni</hi> Chaṭṭarasa, Kūcharsa and <hi rend="italic">sāhaṇi</hi> Nāraṇadēva.</p>						

						</summary>
